{
  "stem": "6966.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At school when I was six, seven years of age, I-- they used to call me in front of the class to sing a song.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from that, that started really to take singing lessons later on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I became in the Music Academy in Rotterdam later on to train my voice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somewhere way back in Russia, as my father told me, there must have been somebody who was a cantor in shul, and probably some of that stuck on to me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was trying to become a concert singer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, the war finished all that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But before that, I became a member of a light opera company in Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I also became a member of the committee of a Jewish club, boys and girls, which started with about a dozen people and grew up within little time over 100 members.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we gave monthly concerts, or some dances, something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was our duty, the members of the committee, to see the girls home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So every, every man then from the committee took six, eight, or 10 girls along, and saw them off to their homes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now it happened during one of the concerts-- and I was on the stage singing a couple of songs-- that a young lady walked in and settled down and listened to me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I didn't know that was to become my wife, Esther van Dam.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She knew I was going to be her husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She told me that later on, but I didn't know yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was introduced to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was on holiday in Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she lived in London.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was born in Rotterdam, but she lived in London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She could-- she was working a firm making clothes for royalty.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
